snippet.title: Yggdra Union: Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Get an extended view of how strategy gameplay mixes with real-time action in this collection of gameplay clips from the release of Yggdra Union for the PSP® system.

Available September 2008.

For more information, visit:
http://www.atlus.com/yggdraunionpsp
